## Troubleshooting

| Problem | Fix |
|---|---|
| Display stays dark | Check wiring; verify `MAX_DEVICES 12` matches your hardware; confirm `FC16_HW` type |
| No WiFi portal appears | Power-cycle the device; portal only opens when no saved network is found (`wifiManager.resetSettings()` in code to force it) |
| MQTT messages not received | Check broker IP in `IPAddress server(...)`, topic string, and that port 1883 is open |
| OTA upload fails | Verify device IP in `upload_port`; confirm device is on the same network |
| Garbled characters | UTF-8 is handled by `utf8AsciiConvert()` — some special characters outside ISO 8859-1 won't render |
| Device sleeps unexpectedly | Normal behaviour 23:00–06:00; verify NTP is syncing correctly via Serial Monitor |
| eduroam won't connect | Only use the pinned WiFiManager commit — do not upgrade the library |

